title: This Bollywood Actress Shared A Special Holi Video For Her Fans & It’s Going Viral
text:
A post shared by Poonam Pandey (@ipoonampandey) on Mar 10, 2017 at 7:57am PST 
Poonam Pandey recently shared a photo of her butt as a teaser of a hot Holi video she had in store for her fans. Yesterday was Holi and the actress did what she promised. Here’s the video that’s going viral! 
LOL. Happy Holi, you guys! 0
